	(descr "CUSTOM provisional landing for Adafruit 3103 (PSP-3000 2-axis planar slider), hand-soldered on the TOP side. 6 generous numbered pads match the schematic's 6-terminal dual-pot symbol (Joystick:PSP_Slider); physically 4 electrical nets (VCC/X/Y/GND) - the two pots share the VCC and GND rails. ~20x20 mm body keep-out (courtyard) + flex-tail exit clearance at bottom. PINOUT IS PROVISIONAL - meter the physical part before soldering (see DESIGN-DECISIONS.md Decision A).")
